rows.label: qev015604_MSG0001
rows.name:
Regina's shop should have ample space to
accommodate it...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0002
rows.name:
You must expand FrontierNav farther into Oblivia,
my friend. You simply must![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0012
rows.name:
Ah, such would be our greatest of pleasures.
We've never been one for sitting and waiting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0003
rows.name:
As your people say, I'll see that no good deed goes
unpublished. I shall pay you back with kindness!
...Also discounts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0004
rows.name:
It's nearly complete. We implore you to find the items
Giogion requested with all haste.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0008
rows.name:
Ah, such would be our greatest of pleasures.
We've never been one for sitting and waiting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0005
rows.name:
Once complete, we're certain our machine will be a
great boon to everyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0006
rows.name:
By all means, please open a new augment slot.
If the attack assault rifle we furnished you with does
not excite you, any equipment will do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015604_MSG0007
rows.name:
Giogion has engineered the device to the very highest
of standards. It works as advertised, or no money back![ST:wait ]
